  <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>The <link linkend="class-ossoabookaccountmodel"><classname>AccountModel</classname></link> is a model that lists the
    <link linkend="class-galagoaccount"><classname>GalagoAccount</classname></link> objects of accounts from
    <classname>evolution.ebook.EContact</classname> objects
    exposed by an <classname>evolution.ebook.EBookView</classname>, and their associated
    <link linkend="class-ossoabookaccountpresence"><classname>AccountPresence</classname></link> objects.</para>
  </refsect1>
